### Epigenetics & epidemiology

Epigenetics offers one way to understand how the varied and complex environments we exist in can become embodied to affect our biology, including our health and risks of disease, disability and death.

The following video introduces how epidemiological approaches can help us to understand the role of epigenetics in health and disease.

